{
  "stem": "19195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but some-- this is-- this is how it went on, day after day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First I wore the dress they gave me, the one I was photographed in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But later on, we were able to get something from the people who worked in the-- they called that the Kanada.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm sure you heard of that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Shoes, when I arrived there-- I'd left my good shoes in that barrack we took showers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never saw those shoes again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- I happened to get two shoes one was still-- both were-- you know, the different-- one was left, and one was-- I mean one was the right, and this was the left.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I walked in those Holland wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was hectic.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when they took us to that-- in Birkenau-- to that-- where they would give us decent clothes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We could pick up from the-- whatever we wanted to, and shoes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they put us on a train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we ended up in Stuttgart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'44.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say about five hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there was a-- a German guard, a-- a lady.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But she saw-- as she was walking to see from car to car how we are doing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was burning up with-- with fever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was delirious.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I heard she's calling there a name.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what she was calling was Rachel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And [PAUSES] she said to her, do you have some aspirins left, the German guard.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She says, yes, I have some.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Why don't you give me-- I want to help out this girl there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She's laying.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She's screaming.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She's so delirious.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Give me some aspirins.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she sat down near me, that German guard.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was humming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was singing a song to herself.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
